Example: To call a Beijing number while in Beijing, enter the number and then select Call other countries. To call another country while outside Korea: Enter the international call code, country code, and the number, and then select Call other countries. You can insert the international call code with a plus sign (press the 0 key) and must remove the first zero from the number. Example: To call 06-1234-5678 from Beijing, China to Osaka, Japan, enter +81-6-1234-5678, and then select Call other countries."
